                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8554" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1324</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1903 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">精益求精：F公司碳会计处理的优化策略探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Exploration of optimization strategy for carbon accounting treatment of F Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许金花，陈星滢，张嘉烨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">F公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">碳排放权会计；会计确认；会计计量；信息披露</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Carbon emission rights accounting、Accounting recognition、Accounting measurement、Information disclosure</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全国统一碳排放权市场建立发展的背景下，《碳排放权交易有关会计处理暂行规定》（下称《暂行规定》）在重点排放企业实际应用中的适用性和有效性有必要进行重新评估。F公司以成为国内领先的绿色低碳综合智慧能源企业集团为战略目标，紧跟绿色低碳经济的发展方向，并在节能减排方面做出积极努力，同时，该公司在会计实践中积极使用《暂行规定》处理碳排放权的相关事项。本案例基于F公司公开的碳排放权变动信息，通过模拟未公开的碳排放权具体业务，阐述了F公司在实施《暂行规定》过程中的账务处理，并指出了在碳会计确认、计量和信息披露方面可能遇到的问题和挑战。本案例通过对F公司现行碳会计处理的批判性思考，帮助学生深入理解碳会计准则，鼓励学生对案例公司实际应用碳会计准则过程中的适用性和局限性提出相应的优化方案，以更好地反映碳业务的经济实质，提高碳排放权信息的披露质量，从而为其他企业在碳会计的实际应用方面提供有益的指导和参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of the establishment and development of a national unified carbon emission rights market, it is necessary to re-evaluate the practical applicability and effectiveness of the Interim Provisions on Accounting Treatment of Carbon Emission Rights Trading (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;Interim Provisions&quot;) for key emission enterprises. With the strategic goal of becoming a leading green and low-carbon comprehensive smart energy enterprise group in China, Company F closely follows the development direction of green and low-carbon economy and makes active efforts in energy conservation and emission reduction. At the same time, the company actively uses the Interim Provisions to deal with matters related to carbon emission rights in its accounting practice. Based on the disclosed carbon emission right change information of Company F, this case describes the accounting treatment of Company F during the implementation of the Interim Provisions by simulating the specific business of the undisclosed carbon emission right, and points out the problems and challenges encountered in carbon accounting recognition, measurement and information disclosure. Through critical thinking on the current carbon accounting treatment of Company F, this case helps students to have a deep understanding of carbon accounting standards, encourages students to express their opinions on the applicability and limitations of carbon accounting standards in the actual application of the case company, and puts forward corresponding optimization plans, so as to provide useful guidance and reference for other enterprises in the practical application of carbon accounting.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">会计确认；会计计量；信息披露</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
